00:00:01.910 --> 00:00:06.230
I bow to all the seekers of Truth.

00:00:08.469 --> 00:00:11.350
Definitely it is evident today

00:00:11.550 --> 00:00:15.269
that you have come here all the way in the rain

00:00:15.590 --> 00:00:20.310
to seek the truth, that you are real seekers.

00:00:25.550 --> 00:00:28.869
And the real seekers

00:00:29.070 --> 00:00:32.270
will find the real way.

00:00:32.470 --> 00:00:38.168
Whatever they may do, whatever wrong path they may take,

00:00:38.369 --> 00:00:42.354
they may identify themselves with wrong things also,

00:00:42.555 --> 00:00:45.282
and may oppose in the beginning the truth,

00:00:45.483 --> 00:00:50.870
but ultimately they will all find the real path,

00:00:51.110 --> 00:00:56.205
as long as they do not try to deceive themselves.

00:01:03.190 --> 00:01:06.628
The awakening of the Kundalini

00:01:06.830 --> 00:01:11.309
is not a new thing as you people may be thinking.

00:01:11.510 --> 00:01:14.909
It has been done since

00:01:15.110 --> 00:01:18.821
sixteenth century back,

00:01:19.022 --> 00:01:24.559
when it is said Indra, the God King,

00:01:24.766 --> 00:01:27.189
was given Realization.

00:01:27.390 --> 00:01:29.164
So you can imagine,

00:01:29.365 --> 00:01:32.583
that is called as Siddhendra,

00:01:32.785 --> 00:01:38.310
means the Indra first made a hole here.

00:01:38.968 --> 00:01:42.869
And there’s a place where it was done in India.

00:01:43.070 --> 00:01:44.716
It’s a very ancient thing,

00:01:44.884 --> 00:01:47.189
and at the time of Rama also,

00:01:47.390 --> 00:01:49.466
there was a fellow called Nachiketa

00:01:49.667 --> 00:01:54.218
who came to Rama’s father-in-law, Janaka,

00:01:54.419 --> 00:01:59.060
and asked Him if he could get his Self Realization.

00:01:59.630 --> 00:02:02.389
And the father-in-law said that

00:02:02.590 --> 00:02:05.989
“You can ask anything but not for your Realization.”

00:02:06.190 --> 00:02:09.459
He said, “No, I don’t want anything else but Realization”.

00:02:09.660 --> 00:02:14.966
And they say that He put him to test, many a times, for years,

00:02:15.167 --> 00:02:18.269
and then he was the first who got Realization,

00:02:18.469 --> 00:02:21.245
at the time of Shri Rama.

00:02:22.027 --> 00:02:28.084
It is very interesting that how this system of Self Realization,

00:02:28.286 --> 00:02:32.398
was kept more or less exclusive, and rather secretive,

00:02:32.599 --> 00:02:36.480
because the people would like always

00:02:36.681 --> 00:02:40.780
to use this method to make some money out of it;

00:02:41.203 --> 00:02:44.551
that they would not respect the reality,

00:02:44.752 --> 00:02:49.769
and would learn, say about your chakras, Kundalini,

00:02:49.970 --> 00:02:53.390
this, that, few words and start selling books

00:02:53.790 --> 00:02:56.790
or posing that they are born again,

00:02:56.973 --> 00:02:59.108
and impressing others with it,

00:02:59.310 --> 00:03:04.268
and try to make some cults or some sort of groups,

00:03:04.469 --> 00:03:07.829
just forming into some falsehood.

00:03:08.258 --> 00:03:11.669
And that is the reason this was kept quite a secret.

00:03:11.870 --> 00:03:16.269
But on the right hand side of the seeking,

00:03:16.469 --> 00:03:20.269
they tried to find out the ways and methods

00:03:20.469 --> 00:03:25.029
how to initiate the elements within us, the casual of elements,

00:03:25.230 --> 00:03:27.989
first to initiate the causal of the elements,

00:03:28.230 --> 00:03:32.429
by which we could control the elements for our own purpose.

00:03:32.630 --> 00:03:36.789
This was one way where they called it as the Yagnya and all that.

00:03:36.990 --> 00:03:39.006
And that’s how the Vedas were written.

00:03:39.207 --> 00:03:42.469
Veda means vida, means to know.

00:03:42.670 --> 00:03:46.123
These were written to say that you have to know.

00:03:46.324 --> 00:03:49.350
And at the very beginning of the Vedas, it is written

00:03:49.670 --> 00:03:52.492
that after reading this book, throughout,

00:03:52.693 --> 00:03:56.124
if you have not known the truth,

00:03:56.267 --> 00:03:59.149
it is of no use to you.

00:03:59.350 --> 00:04:02.909
The very first stanza says so.

00:04:03.110 --> 00:04:05.780
So the whole thing was done with that idea,

00:04:05.982 --> 00:04:09.097
and in the ancient country of India,

00:04:09.298 --> 00:04:11.433
they started working on the right side

00:04:11.634 --> 00:04:15.158
to know this subtle body

00:04:15.373 --> 00:04:18.654
or the subtle Deities of all the elements

00:04:18.855 --> 00:04:22.230
so that they could master the elements; this was first idea.

00:04:22.469 --> 00:04:27.183
On the left hand side, they started another kind of a search,

00:04:27.384 --> 00:04:30.270
in believing that there is God,

00:04:30.470 --> 00:04:32.910
and we have to ask the help of God.

00:04:33.150 --> 00:04:36.243
And they started praying,

00:04:36.442 --> 00:04:38.509
first to Primordial Mother,

00:04:38.710 --> 00:04:42.869
because in every religion there is a place for the Mother.

00:04:43.070 --> 00:04:47.989
There’s no religion which does not believe in the Primordial Mother.

00:04:48.190 --> 00:04:50.910
You can say that at the time of Mohammed Sahib,

00:04:51.190 --> 00:04:54.629
He didn’t talk much about it, because the time was such.

00:04:54.830 --> 00:04:56.699
But His own daughter

00:04:56.900 --> 00:04:59.937
was an incarnation of the Primordial Mother,

00:05:00.128 --> 00:05:01.909
whose name was Fatima Bi.

00:05:02.110 --> 00:05:06.401
And the two sons that were born to Her, are the sons

00:05:06.603 --> 00:05:12.636
who came on this earth also as Mahavira and Buddha.

00:05:12.837 --> 00:05:14.863
And they were born even earlier.

00:05:15.064 --> 00:05:17.515
Like that, they were born again and again,

00:05:17.716 --> 00:05:21.870
as these two elements, as the disciples, as two disciples.

00:05:22.150 --> 00:05:25.531
And you can see if you read their life,

00:05:25.732 --> 00:05:29.029
their character, their behavior, you’ll be surprised,

00:05:29.230 --> 00:05:32.669
how these two characters have been born again and again,

00:05:32.870 --> 00:05:37.110
in different times, to suggest two personalities

00:05:37.310 --> 00:05:40.389
of two types, who have been seeking God,

00:05:40.590 --> 00:05:44.032
and who have been trying to understand God

00:05:44.233 --> 00:05:46.591
through their personality as disciples;

00:05:46.793 --> 00:05:50.069
and how they reached a conclusion

00:05:50.270 --> 00:05:55.030
after taking a kind of a position in life.

00:05:55.270 --> 00:05:57.830
Now for example Buddha preached that

00:05:58.031 --> 00:06:00.629
there should be complete non-violence,

00:06:00.870 --> 00:06:05.096
and also Mahavira said so, there should be non-violence.

00:06:05.297 --> 00:06:07.630
But they carried it to such an extent.

00:06:07.831 --> 00:06:11.401
that Mahavira’s disciples started saving the bugs.

00:06:11.602 --> 00:06:14.713
They would get some bugs from the village,

00:06:14.968 --> 00:06:16.737
put them in a hut

00:06:16.938 --> 00:06:20.949
and put a Brahmin inside that – fanaticism at that stage -

00:06:21.150 --> 00:06:23.050
and the bugs would eat,

00:06:23.241 --> 00:06:29.469
or take, take out the blood of that poor brahmin,

00:06:29.670 --> 00:06:32.789
and when they would be all filled with blood,

00:06:32.990 --> 00:06:35.829
then they would give money to this brahmin.

00:06:36.030 --> 00:06:41.549
Such extreme vegetarianism or extreme type of ahinsa!

00:06:41.750 --> 00:06:44.468
Or another type of Buddha’s ahinsa that started

00:06:44.710 --> 00:06:47.269
that Buddha was not the one who was a vegetarian,

00:06:47.469 --> 00:06:49.990
because He died, at the end you know that,

00:06:50.230 --> 00:06:54.189
He ate the meat of a boar which was not properly cooked.

00:06:54.469 --> 00:06:58.412
So this kind of extreme type of

00:06:58.613 --> 00:07:02.468
food-oriented religion started out of them,

00:07:02.670 --> 00:07:06.088
so they got themselves born again,

00:07:06.390 --> 00:07:11.427
as Hassan and Hussein and (unclear)

00:07:12.025 --> 00:07:15.188
that when it come to righteousness,

00:07:15.351 --> 00:07:19.081
when it comes to the (fight) for righteousness, you have to fight.

00:07:19.282 --> 00:07:21.572
That time the one who doesn't fight

00:07:21.794 --> 00:07:25.509
is not a person who is a religious person.

00:07:25.710 --> 00:07:32.377
So the idea of all these people was in such a way

00:07:32.578 --> 00:07:37.527
that the time at that period was such and such,

00:07:37.728 --> 00:07:41.829
and at that period this was the proper thing to be done.

00:07:42.030 --> 00:07:44.910
Now we can see the example of Christ is.

00:07:45.150 --> 00:07:46.782
Christ came at a time

00:07:46.983 --> 00:07:50.629
where the Son of God had to manifest.

00:07:50.830 --> 00:07:55.310
And He came at a time where He had to forgive,

00:07:55.510 --> 00:08:01.430
and He had to show to people how stupid they were, to crucify Him,

00:08:01.630 --> 00:08:06.430
so that they could repent for what stupidity they have done.

00:08:06.631 --> 00:08:08.790
And that’s how He came on this earth.

00:08:09.037 --> 00:08:11.640
But when He will come again,

00:08:11.897 --> 00:08:14.669
He’s not going to come in that way.

00:08:14.870 --> 00:08:17.444
The Second Advent of Christ,

00:08:17.573 --> 00:08:20.829
is going to be a very serious one.

00:08:21.030 --> 00:08:25.110
When He will come, He will have eleven destroying powers.

00:08:25.350 --> 00:08:28.469
With that He will destroy all that is useless,

00:08:28.670 --> 00:08:32.030
all that has gone wasted, all those fanatics

00:08:32.230 --> 00:08:34.726
or "Whom they'll call Christ, Christ&gt;&gt;, I won’t know,

00:08:34.927 --> 00:08:36.390
He’s told that, very well.

00:08:36.591 --> 00:08:39.830
All these things He’s going to absolutely finish off.

00:08:40.070 --> 00:08:43.750
And those who are realized souls,

00:08:43.951 --> 00:08:47.269
who have entered into the Kingdom of God, will be only saved.

00:08:47.469 --> 00:08:51.030
And this is what is described in all the Scriptures.

00:08:51.270 --> 00:08:55.417
Of course somebody calls them, say Islam calls it “Mahdi”

00:08:55.618 --> 00:08:58.110
in India He is called as “Kalki”,

00:08:58.311 --> 00:09:01.790
in the Bible He is called as “the Christ on the white horse”.

00:09:01.991 --> 00:09:03.590
He is called by various names,

00:09:03.830 --> 00:09:06.310
but it is definite that He is going to come,

00:09:06.510 --> 00:09:07.955
and when He comes,

00:09:08.156 --> 00:09:12.884
then He is not going to bother as to tell you, and convince you,

00:09:13.085 --> 00:09:18.104
and to counsel you or to redeem you and give you Realization.

00:09:18.398 --> 00:09:21.469
That time, He is not going to bother about it.

00:09:21.710 --> 00:09:24.430
He is going to come in pure destructive form,

00:09:24.670 --> 00:09:27.241
where He will destroy all that is useless.

00:09:27.442 --> 00:09:31.953
And to understand this, if you see
the Sistine Chapel of Michelangelo,

00:09:32.155 --> 00:09:35.110
you can see Him clearly standing, at the Agnya chakra,

00:09:35.390 --> 00:09:38.069
with a robust body, throwing people up and down.

00:09:38.271 --> 00:09:40.790
Those who call, “Christ, Christ”, He throws them down,

00:09:41.150 --> 00:09:45.757
because they did not do anything what Christ has asked for.

00:09:46.469 --> 00:09:48.368
Now the people should know

00:09:48.569 --> 00:09:51.630
what we have got out of anything whatsoever.

00:09:51.870 --> 00:09:55.350
You may be identified with any cult, with any idea,

00:09:55.550 --> 00:09:57.310
with any group, or anything,

00:09:57.510 --> 00:10:00.828
but always must know what you have you got out of it.

00:10:01.030 --> 00:10:05.189
For example, I would say for Christians it is necessary to know

00:10:05.469 --> 00:10:08.190
that Christ has said a very strong thing,

00:10:08.430 --> 00:10:11.950
“Thou shalt not have adulterous eyes.”

00:10:12.590 --> 00:10:15.790
Let us find out, do we have innocent eyes?

00:10:16.030 --> 00:10:19.108
If we don’t, we are not Christians.

00:10:19.310 --> 00:10:21.310
How do we have innocent eyes?

00:10:21.510 --> 00:10:24.468
How do we develop our innocence, is the problem.

00:10:24.670 --> 00:10:28.749
And to develop our innocence we have to awaken the Kundalini.

00:10:28.950 --> 00:10:30.935
When the Kundalini is awakened, the first center

00:10:31.136 --> 00:10:34.269
of innocence is awakened.

00:10:34.469 --> 00:10:39.789
At that time all the excretion work of the body just stops,

00:10:39.990 --> 00:10:46.484
and this center of Mooladhara, informs the Kundalini,

00:10:46.685 --> 00:10:50.750
that “There is somebody who knows the job and You can rise.”

00:10:50.990 --> 00:10:53.030
Then only the Kundalini rises.

00:10:53.270 --> 00:10:57.251
This center of innocence is first awakened within us.

00:10:57.453 --> 00:11:02.789
If this center finds that the person is anti-God,

00:11:02.991 --> 00:11:05.110
he is anti-Christ,

00:11:05.710 --> 00:11:09.590
he is a man who is a devil, or any sort of a thing,

00:11:09.830 --> 00:11:12.350
it just does not allow the Kundalini to rise.

00:11:12.550 --> 00:11:15.590
I have seen people with absolute frozen Kundalini;

00:11:15.791 --> 00:11:19.230
I have seen people who have nothing to do with Kundalini,

00:11:19.469 --> 00:11:21.395
we can say they are just like devils

00:11:21.596 --> 00:11:25.429
and they have no way that they can be realized.

00:11:25.630 --> 00:11:29.015
But ninety-nine percent people in this world

00:11:29.150 --> 00:11:32.670
are excellent people, good people,

00:11:32.872 --> 00:11:35.150
and out of them I think at least

00:11:35.390 --> 00:11:38.189
thirty to forty percent people are seeking God.

00:11:38.430 --> 00:11:42.790
Not all; some are seeking money, some are seeking power

00:11:43.030 --> 00:11:46.150
and some are seeking some personal indulgences.

00:11:46.430 --> 00:11:50.070
But there are definitely true seekers on this earth,

00:11:50.271 --> 00:11:54.197
and this thirty percent people are, or forty percent people,

00:11:54.398 --> 00:11:57.789
are the most important people from the God’s point of view.

00:11:57.990 --> 00:12:01.590
You might be anything. You might be having any organization,

00:12:01.790 --> 00:12:04.269
you might be having any position in life,

00:12:04.469 --> 00:12:08.030
you might be any great personality, makes no difference to God.

00:12:08.230 --> 00:12:11.469
What is important is that are you seeking?

00:12:11.990 --> 00:12:15.350
If you’re not, the door will be opened has been promised.

00:12:15.550 --> 00:12:17.870
But if you think you have already achieved it

00:12:18.110 --> 00:12:20.909
and that you are there, how can it be worked out?

00:12:21.110 --> 00:12:25.430
So one has to be humble about it, and allow the Kundalini to rise

00:12:25.630 --> 00:12:29.318
in Its own glory, giving you your real beauty.

00:12:29.630 --> 00:12:34.189
Now the thing we have to know that

00:12:34.430 --> 00:12:39.469
as the Kundalini ascends, we also start getting powers.

00:12:39.670 --> 00:12:43.269
The first power is that of innocence.

00:12:43.469 --> 00:12:48.577
Innocence has a power above all other powers.

00:12:48.778 --> 00:12:50.789
It’s the most powerful thing,

00:12:50.990 --> 00:12:53.572
but in the human beings it takes time

00:12:53.773 --> 00:12:57.025
for innocence to be awakened in the full way.

00:12:57.226 --> 00:13:00.549
It takes time. As a child they have the innocence;

00:13:00.790 --> 00:13:03.710
and in childhood, if they get their awakening

00:13:03.990 --> 00:13:06.269
that’s the best thing that can happen to human beings

00:13:06.469 --> 00:13:09.790
that in the childhood only they become, get their Realization.

00:13:10.030 --> 00:13:11.909
But as soon as you start growing

00:13:12.150 --> 00:13:16.029
your attention starts going either to the left or to the right.

00:13:16.230 --> 00:13:18.990
You start indulging into all kinds of things

00:13:19.230 --> 00:13:21.070
as far as your sex is concerned,

00:13:21.310 --> 00:13:23.878
as far as your seeking is concerned,

00:13:24.079 --> 00:13:27.929
and you then jump on to some sort of a wrong thing

00:13:28.130 --> 00:13:29.792
which you should not have done.

00:13:29.993 --> 00:13:32.642
And that’s how the first center gets lost.

00:13:32.843 --> 00:13:36.910
An innocent person is looked after by angels.

00:13:37.270 --> 00:13:40.092
Such a person has no fear of anything.

00:13:40.294 --> 00:13:44.400
He’s not bothered, he’s never violent, he’s never hasty,

00:13:44.630 --> 00:13:47.549
he’s never in a temper, he’s so peaceful,

00:13:47.790 --> 00:13:51.990
and he knows that what he is doing is the right thing.

00:13:52.270 --> 00:13:55.468
Such a person stands by righteousness.

00:13:56.230 --> 00:13:59.789
Like you can see in the life of Christ is a very good example

00:14:00.030 --> 00:14:04.395
that when Mary Magdalene was stoned by people, He stood up,

00:14:04.597 --> 00:14:07.629
and He said, “Among you who has done no sin

00:14:07.830 --> 00:14:09.469
can throw the stone at her.”

00:14:09.670 --> 00:14:12.630
Actually Christ had nothing to do with a prostitute.

00:14:12.870 --> 00:14:16.390
He had no relationship of any kind with her.

00:14:16.590 --> 00:14:20.469
She is a prostitute and He is the Son of God.

00:14:20.670 --> 00:14:24.469
But at that time He did feel that she has a right to exist,

00:14:24.710 --> 00:14:27.550
because those who are stoning her

00:14:27.751 --> 00:14:30.230
are the people who have committed also sins.

00:14:30.469 --> 00:14:34.269
Only she is a person who’s exposed, and He stood by her.

00:14:34.529 --> 00:14:37.042
And that is what happens to a person who is innocent

00:14:37.243 --> 00:14:38.428
he is fearless.

00:14:38.629 --> 00:14:40.350
He has no fear of anything,

00:14:40.550 --> 00:14:44.870
because he knows that he stands on truth and on innocence.

00:14:45.230 --> 00:14:51.070
Such a person also has a capacity to bear up lots of nonsense,

00:14:51.390 --> 00:14:55.990
to laugh at lots of tortures and troubles people bestow upon him.

00:14:56.230 --> 00:14:58.643
And the greatest thing of innocence is,

00:14:58.889 --> 00:15:00.749
that it gives you discretion.

00:15:00.950 --> 00:15:04.444
Such a person is immensely discreet. He’s so wise.

00:15:04.645 --> 00:15:07.829
He may be a little child, he may be a grown-up person,

00:15:08.150 --> 00:15:10.949
he may be a villager, he might be educated,

00:15:11.151 --> 00:15:14.229
he might be uneducated, but he’s so wise

00:15:14.430 --> 00:15:18.476
that he sees what is right and what is righteous.

00:15:19.110 --> 00:15:22.269
And this is the greatest quality of an innocent person,

00:15:22.469 --> 00:15:25.150
that he’s very discreet about everything.

00:15:25.390 --> 00:15:29.710
His discretion is just like a straight forward hit.

00:15:29.950 --> 00:15:32.989
He doesn’t have to think, he doesn’t have to bother.

00:15:33.190 --> 00:15:36.469
Whatever he decides is absolute discreet,

00:15:36.670 --> 00:15:38.549
and he doesn’t have to have choices.

00:15:38.750 --> 00:15:41.980
He doesn’t go on choosing people, he doesn’t go on choosing things.

00:15:42.181 --> 00:15:44.109
He said, “This is the thing” – finished.

00:15:44.310 --> 00:15:47.269
So, such a person becomes absolutely dynamic

00:15:47.469 --> 00:15:51.269
because he doesn’t waste any energy, he doesn’t waste his brains,

00:15:51.469 --> 00:15:54.350
he doesn’t waste his arguments with anyone.

00:15:54.550 --> 00:15:57.110
If he thinks a person is worth arguing, he’ll argue,

00:15:57.350 --> 00:16:00.869
otherwise he’ll say, “All right, you are clever. Go ahead.”

00:16:01.070 --> 00:16:05.379
This is the understanding of a person,

00:16:05.580 --> 00:16:07.350
who is completely discreet.

00:16:07.550 --> 00:16:11.070
Like there was a very big joke about it, that

00:16:11.990 --> 00:16:15.630
there was a man who was going up the road,

00:16:16.510 --> 00:16:20.629
up the stairs, and another one was coming downstairs.

00:16:20.830 --> 00:16:24.870
The one who was going up the road was a wise man

00:16:25.110 --> 00:16:27.669
and the one who was coming down was not a wise man.

00:16:27.870 --> 00:16:30.989
So he tried to be aggressive, so, and he told him

00:16:31.190 --> 00:16:35.749
that “I will not move for you, because I don’t move for fools.”

00:16:35.950 --> 00:16:40.410
So the other one moved on one side and he said, “I do.”

00:16:40.990 --> 00:16:43.950
Meaning, “I move out for fools,”

00:16:44.190 --> 00:16:46.268
you see, but he said, “I do.” And he moved out.

00:16:46.469 --> 00:16:50.589
So he has such a discretion – how far to go and how far not to go.

00:16:50.790 --> 00:16:52.830
Now, I will give you an example how

00:16:53.070 --> 00:16:55.590
in nature you can find this very easily.

00:16:55.830 --> 00:16:58.949
See, the root has a little root cap.

00:16:59.150 --> 00:17:01.110
It’s a very, very small minute thing,

00:17:01.350 --> 00:17:03.269
you have to see through the microscope.

00:17:03.469 --> 00:17:06.195
Now this root cap is a wise thing.

00:17:06.469 --> 00:17:09.799
It goes in the soil, it sees there are some stones,

00:17:10.000 --> 00:17:11.588
so it goes around the stones.

00:17:11.789 --> 00:17:14.868
Then it finds there are boulders. It goes around the boulders.

00:17:15.069 --> 00:17:17.405
It has to find its way, so it's not bothered.

00:17:17.607 --> 00:17:19.309
“You are a boulder? All right, doesn’t matter,

00:17:19.517 --> 00:17:20.943
I am not going to fight with you.”

00:17:21.144 --> 00:17:24.539
It passes through that, it goes directly

00:17:24.740 --> 00:17:27.550
to that place where it has to arrive,

00:17:27.790 --> 00:17:31.080
and when it reaches that place, when he arrives that place,

00:17:31.282 --> 00:17:34.802
what happens, he finds that he has tied up these boulders

00:17:35.004 --> 00:17:38.510
around himself to support the whole tree.

00:17:39.306 --> 00:17:44.190
This is the wisdom of a little bit, small little cell

00:17:44.430 --> 00:17:47.310
which is the root-end.

00:17:47.510 --> 00:17:51.430
So you can imagine how much there is wisdom

00:17:51.630 --> 00:17:55.269
in a little cell like that.

00:17:55.469 --> 00:17:58.430
And God has given us such a good brain

00:17:58.630 --> 00:18:00.870
and if we do not have discretion

00:18:01.110 --> 00:18:03.269
we are like people who are blind,

00:18:03.469 --> 00:18:06.909
who walk without knowing where they have to go.

00:18:07.110 --> 00:18:13.190
So the first power of your innocence is awakened.

00:18:13.670 --> 00:18:16.030
Innocent men cannot be harmed.

00:18:16.270 --> 00:18:20.268
Those who try to harm the innocent men are harmed ultimately.

00:18:20.469 --> 00:18:25.070
They are very severely harmed, and it is amazing sometimes

00:18:25.310 --> 00:18:28.710
that the harm can be too much, too severe

00:18:28.950 --> 00:18:31.830
and that’s why the compassion of Christ thought of it,

00:18:32.070 --> 00:18:34.590
and He said, “Oh God, please forgive them,

00:18:34.791 --> 00:18:37.230
for they do not know what they are doing.”

00:18:37.469 --> 00:18:39.469
Because it could have been that

00:18:39.710 --> 00:18:41.430
with the Father who is so wrathful,

00:18:41.630 --> 00:18:44.269
they would have been all destroyed completely.

00:18:44.469 --> 00:18:47.268
So the way He said, “Forgive them,

00:18:47.469 --> 00:18:49.830
because I do not want

00:18:50.070 --> 00:18:52.270
that these people, who are ignorant people,

00:18:52.470 --> 00:18:55.910
who have tortured Me like this, should be destroyed.”

00:18:56.270 --> 00:18:59.920
This is the sign of innocence.

00:19:00.550 --> 00:19:05.509
Then the second chakra, when it is awaken within you,

00:19:05.710 --> 00:19:11.181
you have a special quality of creativity.

00:19:11.750 --> 00:19:14.269
Because when the second chakra is awaken,

00:19:14.469 --> 00:19:18.358
you are actually thoughtless, there’s no thought in your mind.

00:19:18.559 --> 00:19:23.049
So you start looking at anything, without thinking.

00:19:23.820 --> 00:19:28.230
You start looking at anything that is created

00:19:28.469 --> 00:19:31.749
without any ripple of thought in your mind.

00:19:31.950 --> 00:19:36.029
Like all that is created round the lake of your mind

00:19:36.230 --> 00:19:42.398
is completely reflected in that ripple-less lake,

00:19:42.599 --> 00:19:48.269
and you see the complete reflection of that creation,

00:19:48.469 --> 00:19:53.269
as well as the joy that is bubbling in that creation.

00:19:53.469 --> 00:19:56.269
So your creativity becomes tremendous.

00:19:56.469 --> 00:19:59.852
You start seeing things, but not thinking about it.

00:20:00.053 --> 00:20:03.269
Now, see if you come to this hall,

00:20:03.469 --> 00:20:05.869
and you start seeing something, you like it,

00:20:06.070 --> 00:20:08.790
then you start thinking, “Oh God, this is a beautiful thing,

00:20:09.070 --> 00:20:12.269
but how much it must have cost? And now how old it is?

00:20:12.469 --> 00:20:15.469
Is it going to last or not? Is it insured or not?”

00:20:15.670 --> 00:20:17.550
All sorts of funny ideas will come to you,

00:20:17.790 --> 00:20:19.734
and you’ll never enjoy what it is.

00:20:19.935 --> 00:20:22.349
But supposing you have no thought about it,

00:20:22.550 --> 00:20:24.269
you just watch it, you just see it.

00:20:24.470 --> 00:20:28.350
What happens? The creation that of the artist

00:20:28.550 --> 00:20:30.389
who has created this beautiful thing,

00:20:30.590 --> 00:20:33.109
the joy of that creation that the artist had -

00:20:33.350 --> 00:20:36.567
who might be dead now - you start enjoying that joy.

00:20:36.768 --> 00:20:41.567
The whole thing can be filled in you with that bubbling joy

00:20:41.768 --> 00:20:45.401
that he wanted to put there with his own heart.

00:20:45.602 --> 00:20:48.510
And that’s what happens because there is no thought.

00:20:48.750 --> 00:20:51.269
So the creativity becomes tremendous.

00:20:51.469 --> 00:20:54.710
But it’s not only that the creativity is tremendous,

00:20:54.911 --> 00:20:56.469
but your techniques even.

00:20:56.670 --> 00:20:59.910
For example, a musician can become a tremendous musician.

00:21:00.150 --> 00:21:04.790
People who have never done any work, can become extremely powerful.

00:21:05.230 --> 00:21:07.869
We have somebody here from India.

00:21:08.070 --> 00:21:09.668
The other day he was telling people,

00:21:09.870 --> 00:21:12.047
because he gave one of the lectures,

00:21:12.248 --> 00:21:14.696
that “I had never seen what is wood is.

00:21:14.897 --> 00:21:18.269
I did not know what was teak, what was other wood and all that.”

00:21:18.469 --> 00:21:20.269
And he had no job when he came to Me.

00:21:20.469 --> 00:21:22.960
And he said, “Now, after Realization what job should I take?”

00:21:23.161 --> 00:21:25.672
I said, “You take to interior decoration”, and he got a shock.

00:21:25.873 --> 00:21:27.469
He said, “I don’t know what (to do).

00:21:27.670 --> 00:21:29.337
How am I to take interior decoration?”

00:21:29.538 --> 00:21:31.750
I said, “You can start feeling the vibrations.

00:21:31.990 --> 00:21:34.630
You just do it on the basis on vibrations.”

00:21:34.870 --> 00:21:37.469
And he did it, and he made a big money out of it,

00:21:37.670 --> 00:21:39.590
because as I told you the other day,

00:21:39.830 --> 00:21:42.710
whatever is absolutely beautiful you think,

00:21:42.950 --> 00:21:45.550
has nothing in it but has vibrations.

00:21:45.790 --> 00:21:48.869
It has a coefficient which gives you vibrations.

00:21:49.070 --> 00:21:51.510
Like Mona Lisa now. We like her, Mona Lisa.

00:21:51.750 --> 00:21:54.109
According to modern standards she cannot be a beauty

00:21:54.350 --> 00:21:57.330
because she was a very plump lady, an elderly lady.

00:21:57.531 --> 00:22:01.030
But today also, if you go there, you cannot see her painting,

00:22:01.270 --> 00:22:04.190
it’s so crowded, everybody’s anxious to see Mona Lisa.

00:22:04.469 --> 00:22:06.269
And if you go and feel the vibrations,

00:22:06.469 --> 00:22:08.269
from distance you’ll get vibrations,

00:22:08.469 --> 00:22:12.270
because the coefficients of her body, face and everything

00:22:12.470 --> 00:22:15.469
is made so well, that you get the vibrations.

00:22:15.830 --> 00:22:19.468
Now people are very anxious to create new ideas,

00:22:19.670 --> 00:22:21.757
new type of things, and these,

00:22:21.958 --> 00:22:24.184
but these things do not sell

00:22:24.385 --> 00:22:27.910
and even if they sell temporarily, they have no eternal values.

00:22:28.190 --> 00:22:31.790
So the people with this chakra enlightened,

00:22:32.030 --> 00:22:37.405
start creating things of very eternal values,

00:22:38.190 --> 00:22:39.718
of universal values.

00:22:39.919 --> 00:22:42.933
Anywhere you take such a thing, you will take it to India,

00:22:43.134 --> 00:22:46.510
you take it to China, you take it to Japan or you take it to America

00:22:46.750 --> 00:22:50.469
anywhere, any human being who sees that,

00:22:50.670 --> 00:22:54.269
sees the beauty of the Spirit,

00:22:54.469 --> 00:22:57.230
because it gives you joy in your Spirit.

00:22:57.469 --> 00:23:01.269
So the pure art is produced (through you).

00:23:01.469 --> 00:23:02.690
That’s the purity,

00:23:02.891 --> 00:23:05.750
or I would say the holy art is produced through you.

00:23:05.990 --> 00:23:09.704
When you start producing that holy art, then you should believe

00:23:09.905 --> 00:23:14.269
that you have got an enlightenment on that chakra.

00:23:14.469 --> 00:23:16.481
This chakra has another capacity,

00:23:16.682 --> 00:23:20.362
to transform your fat, for the use of your brain.

00:23:20.563 --> 00:23:24.350
And it works very hard for that, when you start thinking too much.

00:23:24.550 --> 00:23:26.392
And by that over thinking,

00:23:26.593 --> 00:23:29.036
what happens, that you develop all the diseases

00:23:29.237 --> 00:23:31.990
of the organs which it has to look after.

00:23:32.230 --> 00:23:34.230
Like, it has to look after the liver,

00:23:34.469 --> 00:23:37.269
it has to look after the pancreas, it has to look after the spleen,

00:23:37.469 --> 00:23:41.470
it has to look after the parts of the intestine and the uterus.

00:23:41.910 --> 00:23:45.437
So what happens that when you use this chakra

00:23:45.638 --> 00:23:49.349
only for the use of thinking and thinking and thinking,

00:23:49.550 --> 00:23:51.830
all these things go out of order.

00:23:52.070 --> 00:23:56.085
And one by one you start developing diseases like diabetes,

00:23:56.286 --> 00:24:00.904
and then you start developing diseases of the stomach,

00:24:01.105 --> 00:24:04.541
and sometimes the spleen, and all other diseases

00:24:04.742 --> 00:24:06.769
which are very dangerous, that the,

00:24:06.920 --> 00:24:09.666
as you can call the blood cancer and all those things,

00:24:09.867 --> 00:24:12.229
out of this kind of mad thinking.

00:24:12.430 --> 00:24:15.510
Now to tell you that you shouldn’t think too much,

00:24:15.750 --> 00:24:18.902
you shouldn’t bother too much, you should not be wobbly,

00:24:19.103 --> 00:24:21.696
you should take things easy, be light-hearted,

00:24:21.897 --> 00:24:23.744
is not possible in the modern times

00:24:23.896 --> 00:24:25.789
because we are slaves of the watch.

00:24:25.990 --> 00:24:30.149
But what happens, that when you get Realization,

00:24:30.350 --> 00:24:32.670
your thinking process becomes regulated.

00:24:32.910 --> 00:24:34.590
You only think when you have to think.

00:24:34.791 --> 00:24:37.269
You just go on thinking, thinking, like horns coming out.

00:24:37.469 --> 00:24:40.589
You don’t think like that. You only think when you have to think.

00:24:40.790 --> 00:24:44.628
And whatever you think comes from you inspiration as such.

00:24:44.830 --> 00:24:48.590
Now for time, you see, My watch is always out of order.

00:24:48.830 --> 00:24:53.468
I deliberately keep it out of order, because the time is

00:24:55.870 --> 00:24:57.510
in your hands.

00:24:57.750 --> 00:25:00.310
Supposing these people will hurry Me up too much,

00:25:00.510 --> 00:25:03.612
“Mother we have go now, we’ll miss
the plane, this thing, that thing.”

00:25:03.813 --> 00:25:05.601
I said, “All right, if you say I’ll go.”

00:25:05.802 --> 00:25:07.498
I go to the airport

00:25:07.699 --> 00:25:09.909
and there they find the plane is three hours late.

00:25:10.110 --> 00:25:12.269
Then they said, “Mother, why didn’t you tell us?”

00:25:12.469 --> 00:25:14.590
I said, “I was telling you, no need to hurry up.

00:25:14.830 --> 00:25:16.349
Why didn’t you telephone and find out?

00:25:16.550 --> 00:25:19.710
If you had telephoned, we would not have been there earlier.”

00:25:19.950 --> 00:25:22.726
So you see, you start seeing

00:25:22.927 --> 00:25:27.399
that this time is best for this, this time is best for that.

00:25:27.600 --> 00:25:29.881
You don’t have to become a slave of the watch.

00:25:30.082 --> 00:25:32.417
Like this, people become such slaves

00:25:32.618 --> 00:25:37.469
that they arrive at a point where there can be

00:25:37.670 --> 00:25:39.710
some sort of a wrong thing happening

00:25:39.950 --> 00:25:43.469
or maybe that you reach the place
and you have to wait for four hours,

00:25:43.710 --> 00:25:47.496
you have to do all kinds of arrangements

00:25:47.697 --> 00:25:49.408
to make yourself comfortable.

00:25:49.609 --> 00:25:52.550
Or sometimes it so happens that you quarrel with your wife,

00:25:52.790 --> 00:25:54.941
quarrel with your husband, quarrel with your children,

00:25:55.142 --> 00:25:56.883
“Oh, we are getting late, we are getting late

00:25:57.084 --> 00:25:58.200
we have to be on the time.”

00:25:58.401 --> 00:26:00.268
All this madness comes to people

00:26:00.469 --> 00:26:02.870
because they have not got their Realization.

00:26:03.110 --> 00:26:05.790
Once you get Realization, you station down.

00:26:06.030 --> 00:26:08.830
You are very much at ease with yourself.

00:26:09.070 --> 00:26:12.189
You don’t hurry others and you don’t trouble others.

00:26:12.430 --> 00:26:15.709
Like small, small things, how much we trouble by our worries.

00:26:15.910 --> 00:26:19.470
You see, human beings will go on saying, “I’m worried.”

00:26:19.710 --> 00:26:22.390
But what’s the use of worrying? Now if I tell you, “Don’t worry”

00:26:22.590 --> 00:26:23.774
you cannot stop it.

00:26:23.976 --> 00:26:25.990
But once the hole is made here,

00:26:26.230 --> 00:26:28.190
which we call the Brahmarandhra is opened,

00:26:28.430 --> 00:26:30.750
then there’s a hole out of which the worry comes out,

00:26:30.990 --> 00:26:32.990
and then you just cannot worry.

00:26:33.230 --> 00:26:35.230
Even if you want to worry, you won’t worry;

00:26:35.469 --> 00:26:40.270
because somehow or other you go beyond that nonsense of worrying.

00:26:40.990 --> 00:26:44.910
In any way, mentally I cannot convince you that you don’t worry.

00:26:45.150 --> 00:26:47.390
But once you get Realization, you’ll be amazed,

00:26:47.590 --> 00:26:49.590
you’ll be just enjoying yourself.

00:26:49.830 --> 00:26:52.310
Even if you are late, you are not going to bother about

00:26:52.510 --> 00:26:54.510
or trouble others and you will find

00:26:54.750 --> 00:26:56.670
that you’ll be are always in time for things,

00:26:56.910 --> 00:26:58.630
because there is a force,

00:26:58.870 --> 00:27:02.150
this All Pervading Power of God looks after you.

00:27:02.390 --> 00:27:04.750
You start believing in it, how it works out.

00:27:04.990 --> 00:27:07.590
You won’t believe how much it helps,

00:27:07.830 --> 00:27:12.070
how much it works out, how it can operate

00:27:12.310 --> 00:27:14.469
just beyond description.

00:27:14.670 --> 00:27:17.116
I mean, I’ll tell you a story which you won’t believe.

00:27:17.324 --> 00:27:20.105
Did I tell them yesterday about the boy who fainted?

00:27:20.280 --> 00:27:22.029
SY: I don't think so, Mother.
SM: No.

00:27:22.230 --> 00:27:24.269
SM: A story about Myself,

00:27:24.469 --> 00:27:27.269
and then a story about Warren I can tell you.

00:27:27.469 --> 00:27:30.190
It’s in the newspaper, so you can believe it.

00:27:30.430 --> 00:27:32.670
I was giving a lecture in Bedford

00:27:32.910 --> 00:27:35.950
and that was from seven to ten

00:27:36.190 --> 00:27:38.710
and about eight o’clock a boy fell down somewhere,

00:27:39.030 --> 00:27:42.269
about I don’t know ten-fifteen miles from a bridge.

00:27:42.469 --> 00:27:45.750
Very deep down he fell down from his motorbike.

00:27:45.990 --> 00:27:48.120
And they sent for an ambulance.

00:27:48.321 --> 00:27:50.640
They got frightened; they thought this boy must be dead,

00:27:50.841 --> 00:27:52.869
to fall down to this extent.

00:27:53.070 --> 00:27:56.270
So the ambulance came in and when the ambulance came in,

00:27:56.470 --> 00:27:58.630
this boy just walked up, and he came up

00:27:58.870 --> 00:28:00.390
and he sat in the ambulance.

00:28:00.590 --> 00:28:02.269
So they said, “How are you?”

00:28:02.469 --> 00:28:04.269
He said “I’m all right, nothing wrong with me.”

00:28:04.469 --> 00:28:06.071
So they said, “But nothing happened to you.”

00:28:06.272 --> 00:28:07.950
He said, “No, I broke lots of things

00:28:08.190 --> 00:28:10.556
but a Lady came in a white clothes,

00:28:10.757 --> 00:28:13.122
in a white Mercedes (that’s My car),

00:28:13.323 --> 00:28:16.469
and She walked down up to me and She cured me.

00:28:16.670 --> 00:28:21.510
And only She left the lower portion of my bone,

00:28:21.750 --> 00:28:23.950
and She said that, You come for this to Me,

00:28:24.151 --> 00:28:26.150
and the rest is I’m perfectly all right, see."

00:28:26.469 --> 00:28:28.190
They couldn’t believe it, you see.

00:28:28.430 --> 00:28:30.790
And the police was there, and everybody was there.

00:28:31.030 --> 00:28:34.917
And the next day he saw My photograph in the newspaper,

00:28:35.118 --> 00:28:36.990
and he informed them, he informed the police,

00:28:37.191 --> 00:28:38.914
“This is the Lady Who came and cured me.”

00:28:39.115 --> 00:28:40.990
So they telephoned our people, and ask them,

00:28:41.230 --> 00:28:42.310
“Did She pass this way that day?”

00:28:42.510 --> 00:28:44.710
They said, “That time She was just giving lecture

00:28:44.950 --> 00:28:47.109
before six hundred people. She was not there.”

00:28:47.310 --> 00:28:50.269
So they were quite amazed, how it has happened. But it can happen.

00:28:50.469 --> 00:28:52.710
It’s nothing new. I mean it has happened many a times.

00:28:53.030 --> 00:28:55.670
But one of these that has appeared in the newspaper is like that.

00:28:55.910 --> 00:28:57.469
Now, how does this happen?

00:28:57.670 --> 00:29:01.110
God has got wonderful television also, perfect,

00:29:01.350 --> 00:29:03.550
it’s so systematic, it’s so scientific.

00:29:03.790 --> 00:29:08.389
How it works, that for that you have to just see and wonder.

00:29:08.590 --> 00:29:12.189
He has got telecommunication, He has got computers,

00:29:12.469 --> 00:29:14.590
He has got everything that you have created,

00:29:14.830 --> 00:29:18.463
but extremely efficient and methodical.

00:29:18.664 --> 00:29:21.349
You don’t have to worry, it just works out.

00:29:21.550 --> 00:29:23.909
There are so many things that have happened,

00:29:24.150 --> 00:29:27.190
like you have heard that Christ gave bread,

00:29:27.430 --> 00:29:30.269
five bread and fish to so many people.

00:29:30.469 --> 00:29:32.710
It’s nothing new to now Sahaja Yogis.

00:29:32.950 --> 00:29:34.469
They have seen this many a times happening,

00:29:34.670 --> 00:29:36.310
in our groups and in our camps.

00:29:36.510 --> 00:29:39.349
But another thing which is not believable

00:29:39.550 --> 00:29:41.590
but it has happened to one Mr. Warren,

00:29:41.830 --> 00:29:43.468
Dr. Warren, who is here from Australia.

00:29:43.710 --> 00:29:47.269
When he came to India and he got his Realization,

00:29:47.469 --> 00:29:48.736
and when he went back he said,

00:29:48.895 --> 00:29:51.845
“I must now start talking about Sahaja Yoga

00:29:52.046 --> 00:29:53.630
and giving Realization to people.”

00:29:53.870 --> 00:29:58.830
And when he went back to Australia there was a petrol crisis.

00:29:59.070 --> 00:30:01.909
And there was no petrol in his car, about to finish,

00:30:02.150 --> 00:30:03.803
so they thought, “Now, what to do?

00:30:04.004 --> 00:30:06.550
We’ll not have any petrol. How to do Mother’s work?”

00:30:06.790 --> 00:30:08.119
So they said, “Lets try.

00:30:08.321 --> 00:30:11.990
We’ll just go wherever we want, we’ll not look at the petrol.”

00:30:12.230 --> 00:30:15.950
And they did this for twenty-one days, continuously,

00:30:16.190 --> 00:30:19.092
and when they went to the petrol pump after twenty-one days,

00:30:19.293 --> 00:30:22.109
because the petrol pumps had opened out,

00:30:22.310 --> 00:30:24.349
the petrol pump fellow said that,

00:30:24.551 --> 00:30:29.269
“There is hardly one liter space there. What am I to fill in?”

00:30:29.469 --> 00:30:32.750
And they were amazed, they did it twenty-one days. It can happen.

