01:04:31.514 --> 01:04:33.073
in a very comfortable way.

01:04:33.273 --> 01:04:35.233
First of all, we must sit comfortably.

01:04:35.434 --> 01:04:39.073
There should be no discomfort and that is distractive.

01:04:39.273 --> 01:04:41.073
So just seat very comfortable.

01:04:41.273 --> 01:04:45.233
And everyone should do it. There is nothing special or anything,

01:04:45.434 --> 01:04:47.798
but you must try to do it and achieve it

01:04:47.925 --> 01:04:50.073
because is not proper not to do it.

01:04:50.274 --> 01:04:51.965
When there is a chance you must do it,

01:04:52.166 --> 01:04:55.073
and it won't be good for others also if you don't want to do it.

01:04:55.273 --> 01:04:59.153
It's nothing, nothing too much for you to do it, it's very simple.

01:04:59.354 --> 01:05:01.593
So put your left hands towards Me like this

01:05:01.834 --> 01:05:04.113
and the right hand you have to use,

01:05:04.314 --> 01:05:06.866
because the left hand is the power of desire

01:05:07.046 --> 01:05:09.982
and the right hand is the power of action.

01:05:10.183 --> 01:05:12.272
And as I told you yesterday,

01:05:12.473 --> 01:05:16.114
that in a village of 6000 people I did not do anything like that.

01:05:16.314 --> 01:05:18.634
Just when I stand up they get Realization

01:05:18.874 --> 01:05:21.273
because they are very simple people in a village.

01:05:21.514 --> 01:05:24.305
But here people are quite complicated, they have problems:

01:05:24.506 --> 01:05:27.952
self-created, society-generated,

01:05:28.153 --> 01:05:30.832
the atmosphere generated, all sorts of things are there.

01:05:31.076 --> 01:05:33.664
Doesn’t matter. So we have to little bit nourish

01:05:33.865 --> 01:05:37.572
our different centers, which is a very easy thing to do,

01:05:37.772 --> 01:05:41.262
and I, as I told you, you try to follow it.

01:05:41.462 --> 01:05:44.138
Now, you have to close your eyes,

01:05:44.338 --> 01:05:47.439
and not to open your eyes because of the Agya Chakra.

01:05:47.640 --> 01:05:48.694
That’s very important.

01:05:48.894 --> 01:05:50.548
Because if your eyes are opened

01:05:50.748 --> 01:05:53.731
I find it difficult to raise your Kundalini.

01:05:53.931 --> 01:05:55.921
You have to keep your eyes completely closed,

01:05:56.121 --> 01:05:57.627
it will help your eyesight also.

01:05:57.827 --> 01:05:59.572
So keep your eyes completely closed.

01:05:59.772 --> 01:06:03.421
You don’t have to open till you are told to open your eyes.

01:06:03.621 --> 01:06:06.250
So you don’t have to worry at all.

01:06:06.454 --> 01:06:10.247
If there is anything tight in your body, somewhere,

01:06:10.447 --> 01:06:13.215
just loosen it a little bit, – will be a good idea,

01:06:13.415 --> 01:06:16.045
so that you don’t feel uncomfortable.

01:06:17.252 --> 01:06:20.101
There’s nothing dangerous happens, never has happened.

01:06:20.546 --> 01:06:23.330
At the most you may feel little hot in the hand,

01:06:23.530 --> 01:06:25.735
at the most, doesn’t matter.

01:06:26.257 --> 01:06:29.342
So now, please close your eyes. Just close your eyes.

01:06:29.542 --> 01:06:32.254
Put your both the hands on your lap towards Me.

01:06:32.454 --> 01:06:35.584
Strain your fingers, stretching towards Me.

01:06:35.785 --> 01:06:39.373
Just put your hands on your lap stretching.

01:06:39.574 --> 01:06:41.683
Now put the right hand...

01:06:41.883 --> 01:06:44.723
Left hand has to be fixed as it is, all the time.

01:06:44.923 --> 01:06:49.580
Now the left hand is to be stretched towards Me,

01:06:49.780 --> 01:06:52.104
stretched towards Me, not towards your own hands,

01:06:52.306 --> 01:06:54.496
but towards Me, straight.

01:06:55.208 --> 01:07:00.979
Now, the right hand has to be lifted and put on your heart.

01:07:01.181 --> 01:07:04.728
Just put it on the left side, on your heart.

01:07:06.966 --> 01:07:10.113
At this point, with all sincerity,

01:07:10.716 --> 01:07:15.648
you have to say or ask a question three times:

01:07:15.849 --> 01:07:19.611
"Mother, am I the Spirit?" - with full confidence.

01:07:19.813 --> 01:07:22.356
First of all, you should not feel guilty at all.

01:07:22.557 --> 01:07:25.262
Forget the past. Forget the past!

01:07:25.462 --> 01:07:26.881
Please, forget the past.

01:07:27.081 --> 01:07:29.421
Just now we are talking about the present.

01:07:29.621 --> 01:07:35.300
So just say: "Mother, am I the Spirit?"

01:07:42.695 --> 01:07:45.218
Three times.

01:07:47.954 --> 01:07:51.271
With full confidence, ask the question.

01:08:01.667 --> 01:08:05.997
Now, put this right hand on your stomach,

01:08:06.198 --> 01:08:08.126
on the left-hand side,

01:08:08.327 --> 01:08:12.378
the center of Swadishtana on the left-hand side.

01:08:14.629 --> 01:08:18.944
Nabhi Chakra, on the Nabhi chakra on the left-hand side.

01:08:21.459 --> 01:08:24.966
This is the center of the primordial master within you.

01:08:25.166 --> 01:08:29.778
And as you are the Spirit, you have to say with full confidence:

01:08:30.066 --> 01:08:34.494
“Mother, I am my own master”.

01:08:34.716 --> 01:08:38.749
“I am my own guru” - you have to assert it.

01:08:39.958 --> 01:08:42.229
So that if you have been to wrong gurus,

01:08:42.430 --> 01:08:44.627
fake gurus, all kinds of cults,

01:08:44.827 --> 01:08:46.899
it will all disappear.

01:08:47.684 --> 01:08:49.388
Please, say ten times:

01:08:49.589 --> 01:08:54.230
"Mother, am I my own guide? Am I my own guru?"

01:08:54.431 --> 01:08:57.639
"Am I my own master?”

01:09:07.542 --> 01:09:10.056
Don’t feel guilty, please, don’t feel guilty.

01:09:10.256 --> 01:09:12.702
Don’t feel guilty.

01:09:15.304 --> 01:09:18.704
Still you are feeling guilty - it’s very wrong.

01:09:24.733 --> 01:09:26.765
Candles.

01:09:28.849 --> 01:09:33.477
Now, put this right hand down below on the stomach.

01:09:33.677 --> 01:09:38.220
Down below the stomach is the Swadishtana on the left-hand side.

01:09:40.061 --> 01:09:44.990
At this point you have to say:

01:09:45.471 --> 01:09:49.262
“Mother, make me the master of the Divine art

01:09:49.463 --> 01:09:51.499
or Divine technique”.

01:09:51.701 --> 01:09:55.267
“Mother, I want to be the master of Divine technique”.

01:09:55.468 --> 01:10:00.193
This is the center of the mastery of Divine technique.

01:10:04.890 --> 01:10:07.361
Better.

01:10:27.131 --> 01:10:30.024
Please, say this six times.

01:10:34.731 --> 01:10:37.329
It's all right.

01:10:41.262 --> 01:10:46.273
Press this hand again onto the heart.

01:10:48.762 --> 01:10:50.586
Now assert here

01:10:50.788 --> 01:10:54.888
(unclear) you have to say it without feeling guilty.

01:10:55.288 --> 01:11:02.283
With full confidence you have to say: “Mother I am the Spirit”.

