01:12:17.160 --> 01:12:21.658
On the neck, on the left-hand side, near the shoulder,

01:12:21.859 --> 01:12:24.739
just put it there and..

01:12:26.112 --> 01:12:28.241
press it hard.

01:12:29.778 --> 01:12:32.396
At this point

01:12:32.597 --> 01:12:36.142
you have to say: “Mother, I’m not guilty”.

01:12:37.407 --> 01:12:40.707
Please, say it: “Mother, I’m not guilty”.

01:12:40.907 --> 01:12:46.127
Sixteen times you have to say: “Mother, I’m not guilty”.

01:12:46.764 --> 01:12:49.516
Heart.

