It's better.

01:13:24.702 --> 01:13:27.500
SY: Yes, it's good.

01:13:39.672 --> 01:13:43.954
Now raise this hand higher onto your forehead across,

01:13:44.154 --> 01:13:45.866
on your forehead across.

01:13:46.066 --> 01:13:53.175
At this point you have to say: “Mother, I forgive everyone”.

01:13:55.035 --> 01:13:56.823
SM: Put the light there I think,

01:13:56.998 --> 01:14:00.811
