01:14:10.052 --> 01:14:12.381
Press it hard.

01:14:22.025 --> 01:14:23.598
Now without feeling guilty,

01:14:23.798 --> 01:14:26.542
put your right hand to the back of your head,

01:14:26.742 --> 01:14:27.928
back of your head,

01:14:28.128 --> 01:14:29.548
and try to press it hard,

01:14:29.748 --> 01:14:31.921
back of your head, just above, yes,

01:14:32.128 --> 01:14:34.932
back of your head. Now, try to pull it.

01:14:35.716 --> 01:14:37.861
Pull the head,

01:14:38.939 --> 01:14:42.787
